---
layout: base.njk
title: SERRE Studio
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">VISUAL ARCHIVE · EXHIBITION · DICTIONARY</p>

    <p class="hero-tagline">
      AI 시대의 이미지를 읽고,<br>
      번역하고, 기록합니다.
    </p>

    <a class="text-link" href="/archive/">
      Enter Archive <span>→</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-image hero-video">
    <video
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
      poster="/assets/hero-gallery.png"
      aria-label="구름과 백조, 꽃과 커튼이 부드럽게 움직이는 SERRE Studio 아카이브"
    >
      <source
        src="/assets/home/hero-serre-loop.mp4"
        type="video/mp4"
      >
    </video>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">SERRE COLLECTIONS</p>
    <h2>이미지 전시와 시각 자료를 둘러보세요.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="category-grid">
    <a href="/archive/">
      <img
        src="/assets/home/category-exhibition.png"
        alt="AI 이미지 전시 Exhibition"
      >
    </a>

    <a href="/visual-dictionary/">
      <img
        src="/assets/home/category-dictionary.png"
        alt="빛, 그림자, 재질과 스타일을 정리한 Visual Dictionary"
      >
    </a>

    <a href="/research-notes/">
      <img
        src="/assets/home/category-cinematic.png"
        alt="필름과 렌즈 프롬프트를 정리한 Cinematic Mood"
      >
    </a>

    <a href="/about/">
      <img
        src="/assets/home/category-about.png"
        alt="SERRE Studio 소개와 문의 About"
      >
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.publicExhibitions.length %}
<section class="home-section">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">RECENT EXHIBITION</p>
    <h2>최근 전시</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="archive-grid">
    {% for item in collections.publicExhibitions | slice(0, 4) %}
      {% include "card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
